languages.text: {n}Учитывая хвастливый нрав воина, поразительно, с каким безразличием произнес он свое "прозвище". Похоже, он еще не достаточно доверяет вам, чтобы сообщить свое "волшебное имя".{/n}
{n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Учитывая хвастливый нрав воина, поразительно, с каким безразличием произнес он свое "прозвище". Похоже, он еще не достаточно доверяет вам, чтобы сообщить свое "волшебное имя".{/n}

languages.text: {n}考虑到他一直以来自吹自擂的态度，他在透露这个名字时，态度冷淡得令人吃惊。看来他还并不够信任你，不愿意透露他真正的名字。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}考虑到他一直以来自吹自擂的态度，他在透露这个魔法之名时，态度冷淡得令人吃惊。看来他还并不够信任你，不愿意透露他真正的魔法之名。{/n}

languages.text: {n}Dada la naturaleza jactanciosa del guerrero, la indiferencia con la que revela su nombre es sorprendente. Parece que no confía en ti lo suficiente como para revelar su nombre verdadero.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Dada la naturaleza jactanciosa del guerrero, la indiferencia con la que revela su «nombre mágico» es sorprendente. Parece que no confía en ti lo suficiente como para revelar el de verdad.{/n}

languages.text: {n}この戦士の自慢げな性格を考えると、彼が自分の名を明かしたときの無関心さには驚かされる。どうやら、真名を明かすほどに、彼はあなたを信頼していないようだ。{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}この戦士の自慢げな性格を考えると、彼が自分の名を明かしたときの無関心さには驚かされる。どうやら、真名を明かすほどに、彼はあなたを信頼していないようだ。{/n}

languages.text: {n}Angesichts des prahlerischen Wesens des Kriegers überrascht dich die Leichtigkeit, mit welcher er seinen Namen offenbart hat. Er scheint dir nicht genug zu vertrauen, um seinen wahren Namen preiszugeben.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Angesichts des prahlerischen Wesens des Kriegers überrascht dich die Leichtigkeit, mit welcher er seinen "magischen Namen" offenbart hat. Er scheint dir nicht genug zu vertrauen, um seinen wahren "magischen Namen" preiszugeben.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Pour un guerrier aussi hâbleur, l'indifférence avec laquelle il a révélé son nom est étonnante. Il semble qu'il ne vous fasse pas suffisamment confiance pour vous confier son véritable nom.{/n}
languages.original_text: {n}Given the warrior's boastful nature, the indifference with which he revealed his name is surprising. It seems he does not trust you enough to disclose his true name.{/n}

traits.locale_text: {n}Pour un guerrier aussi hâbleur, l'indifférence avec laquelle il a révélé son « nom magique » est étonnante. Il semble qu'il ne vous fasse pas suffisamment confiance pour vous confier la vérité.{/n}

languages.text: {n}Savaşçının kibirli doğası nedeniyle adını söylerken takındığı umursamaz tavır şaşırtıcı geliyor. Sana gerçek ismini söyleyecek kadar güvenmiyor.{/n}
